\pard\plain \intbl\itap1\sa160\qj{\f1\fs20\b1 Quick Tip}{\f0\fs22  Storytelling relies on strategic and selective emphasis on important events or scenes. Biblical stories are not random collections of events or partial reminiscences about ancient figures\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 they are scenes in a larger narrative, carefully crafted to demonstrate God\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s faithfulness to His people. The events of Abram\u8217\'92s life presented in Genesis represent important milestones in Abram and Sarai\u8217\'92s journey of faith.}
\par\plain \intbl\itap1\f0\fs24\cell{
\trowd\trgaph0 \trautofit1\lastrow \trbrdrt\brdrnil \trbrdrr\brdrnil \trbrdrb\brdrnil \trbrdrl\brdrnil 
